data.description: Welcome to this Cute 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in the center of Port St lucie and mins to Beach's, St Lucie West and more.   This home offers an Open floor plan with Spacious kitchen that overlooks the Large Kitchen nook. With just a little tic and updating this home will have instant equity for the homeowner or investor looking for their next investment.  Out back you have a large fenced yard and covered back porch.  Come take a look and make this your next Purchase!
